{"tid":1819123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港民研：林鄭月娥及鄭若驊最新支持率分別為14%和8%","createTime":"2020-01-10T13:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T03:58:53.000Z","uid":212626,"like":368,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"5a113bcdb0c8a31513cc287fad1894756e6fca85","tid":1819123,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究計劃公布，最新調查顯示，特首林鄭月娥的評分為21.5分，其支持率為14%，反對率為80%，民望淨值為負66個百分點，全部數字與兩周前分別不大。<br />\n<br />\n司長方面，政務司司長張建宗的支持度評分為25.3分，支持率為14%，反對率為54%，民望淨值為負41個百分點，其評分和民望淨值均創其上任以來新低。財政司司長陳茂波的支持度評分為27.6分，支持率為18%，反對率為56%，民望淨值為負37個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n至於律政司司長鄭若驊，其支持度評分為14.5分，<span style=\"color: red;\">支持率為8%，反對率為77%，民望淨值為負69個百分點</span>。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄、民政事務局局長劉江華、陳茂波及張建宗屬於「表現失敗」，<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭月娥、鄭若驊及保安局局長李家超屬於「表現拙劣」</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2351732/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2351732%2F&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=6d9f07cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2351732/</a>"},{"pid":"984d466f0f5eeb879d7d43ca0f5e607ce27d786e","tid":1819123,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49eacb9fae10031dfd9141e7690ea68f333e2e2a","tid":1819123,"uid":212626,"like":119,"dislike":0,"score":119,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊可以自刎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2135e8a465a17307edb94459533dcc5574696dbc","tid":1819123,"uid":297997,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"我比-100分"},{"pid":"9226807b1ef17a8c3cefa6957faac27a3f912b7e","tid":1819123,"uid":229916,"like":163,"dislike":0,"score":163,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:40:25.000Z","msg":"民意逆轉左未<img src=\"/as