img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5194835a155e6359024ac550fbd7b188e22d7e4a","tid":1819123,"uid":247493,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借少少位<br />\n<br />\n🎉 1.11全城連儂日 🎉<br />\n        「勇武感謝祭2020」<br />\n<br />\nPart One - 元祖慶典<br />\n時間：14:00 - 17:00<br />\n地點：金鐘元祖連儂牆<br />\n<br />\nPart Two - 遍地連儂 <br />\n時間：19:00 - 22:00<br />\n地點：全港18區<br />\n<br />\n@Lennonovazed_channel<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n111連儂日To Do List<br />\n-自備文宣及張貼工具(少量) <br />\n-時刻警覺，勿俾狗咬<br />\n-Be water，隨時全身而退<br />\n-為街坊打氣<br />\n-幫手印貼紙派俾手足<br />\n-寫Memo 抒發心中所感所想<br />\n<br />\nRemark: <br />\n-歡迎喺恆常你農場範圍以外嘅地方張貼 實行遍地連儂開花<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4go03h9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4go03h9.jpg&h=181549c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdSMYRu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdSMYRu.jpg&h=dab730c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0352a688f6fa3d819a8a369ed0d59d9dd6147076","tid":1819123,"uid":274722,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"被問到民意有何準則，很多人上街抗議是否其中一個準則，林太說「如果要發生，大家會感覺到這就是主流民意，以往發生過，亦有問責官員因此而請辭」，所以現階段不需要以「數字」作一個定義。"},{"pid":"b8d2505c9f59c66fac8469d2ffd21e9d0ee61398","tid":1819123,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15d5745b998fb1f33c7864560209f009a0468221","tid":1819123,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aeca43ae70401e8fa25307dcfbc9260ab375c82f","tid":1819123,"uid":128923,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"9226807b1ef17a8c3cefa6957faac27a3f912b7e","tid":1819123,"uid":229916,"like":163,"dislike":0,"score":163,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:40:25.000Z","msg":"民意逆轉左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2