like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究計劃公布，最新調查顯示，特首林鄭月娥的評分為21.5分，其支持率為14%，反對率為80%，民望淨值為負66個百分點，全部數字與兩周前分別不大。<br />\n<br />\n司長方面，政務司司長張建宗的支持度評分為25.3分，支持率為14%，反對率為54%，民望淨值為負41個百分點，其評分和民望淨值均創其上任以來新低。財政司司長陳茂波的支持度評分為27.6分，支持率為18%，反對率為56%，民望淨值為負37個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n至於律政司司長鄭若驊，其支持度評分為14.5分，<span style=\"color: red;\">支持率為8%，反對率為77%，民望淨值為負69個百分點</span>。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄、民政事務局局長劉江華、陳茂波及張建宗屬於「表現失敗」，<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭月娥、鄭若驊及保安局局長李家超屬於「表現拙劣」</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2351732/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2351732%2F&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=6d9f07cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2351732/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"官員應該按評分出糧,負多少分按就百分比扣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975d30377f3eb493fb4ab26b5710ef0aec025301","tid":1819123,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:08:07.000Z","msg":"叻哥: 哩啲你信嘅啫"},{"pid":"2e2ed4297203741ca14519a1f44aa9f07dd37650","tid":1819123,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3da4503af4127999e6a442234ac30683823f24","tid":1819123,"uid":283436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"咁撚多？"},{"pid":"1eb4324accd0a12aea24dfdb4cd34a1e6d9442e9","tid":1819123,"uid":136768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T15:15:22.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：問責制"}]}